-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a671c94 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a671c94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Schistosomiasis<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-470fa25 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"470fa25\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-3325a32\" data-id=\"3325a32\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33719e8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"33719e8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Basics<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Parasite: Schistosoma<\/li><li>Generally Seen in Migrants\/Travelers From Endemic Areas (Sub-Saharan Africa)<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Presentation<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Acute Presentation:<ul><li>Swimmer\u2019s Itch &amp; Maculopapular Rash<\/li><li>Katayama Syndrome (Systemic Hypersensitivity Reaction)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Chronic Presenta